    <h1>Content Delivery Network (CDN)</h1>
    <p class="description">A globally distributed edge-server network that reduces page latency by <strong>30-70%</strong>. Directly improves Core Web Vitals and is the single most cost-effective performance investment for any site with a distributed audience.</p>
