        <p>Our SEO audit runs edge tests from 6 continents, checks cache hit ratios, and verifies your Cache-Control headers against Google's page-experience thresholds. When misconfigurations surface, we send back the exact settings to change — with expected LCP delta so you can prioritise engineering time.</p>

